titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on Y3-4,5-dihydro-isoxazol-3-yl)-4-methylsulfonyl-2-methylpheny l?(5-hydroxy-1-methyl-1H-pyrazole-4-yl) methanone.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary: 12/13/2007--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on Y3-4,5-dihydro-isoxazol-3-yl)-4-methylsulfonyl-2-methylpheny l?(5-hydroxy-1-methyl-1H-pyrazole-4-yl) methanone.
